Correspondence with: Sally Adams; Dwight Akers; Charles B.
					 Barker; Yvonne Belmont (Gregory); Julie Bidou; Homer Brown; Terrence Burrow;
					 Ken Carter; Norman Cohen; Al Cox; and Marian Curtis

Correspondence with: Indiana University (George List);
					 Instituto Indigenista Nacional (Jorge Luis Arriola); Norma Keleti; Mr. D.
					 Joshlin; Edgar C. Leaycraft; George Lennon; Liberty Mutual; Seymour B. Liebman;
					 Alan Lomax; and Ben Gray Lumpkin

Correspondence with: Mrs. Guy Manley; Mrs. John T. Manning;
					 [?] Manning; Archie Musick; New American Library (E.L. Doctorow); Tom Paxton;
					 Joe Nicholas; Royal McBee Corp.; Clem Richardson; Nathan Resnick; Mrs. Peter R.
					 [Paris]; Joseph Opperman; Dan O'Meara; Raymond Olitt; William Oliver

