					 Dragoon lyrics (3 songs); 
				  A Sampler of Japanese
					 Songs pamphlet (32 pp.); 
				  The Old Settler
				  placemat from the Acres of Clams Restaurant (1 p.); and photo copystand copies
				  (3" by 4", 31 images)

Contains the following items: 3 typed/handwritten track
